Summary
----------------------------------------------------------------------
This testcase exercises for VC Lint rule "SYN_STMT_UNSYNTH_FOREVER" which flags when 
there is a unsynthasizable construct used in the design. This testcase represents a scenario 
which is used a unsynthasizable consrunct in the design.

Testcase Details
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Design      : forever_loop_in_always.v
VC Lint     : vc_lint.tcl
Command     : make lint 
